text: Cover Up is a 1991 American British Israeli action movie directed by Manny Coto and starring Dolph Lundgren, Louis Gossett Jr., John Finn, Peter Gilmore, Lisa Berkley, John Saint Ryan. ==Other websites== * * Category:1991 action movies Category:1990s American action movies Category:British action movies Category:Israeli movies Category:Movies set in Israel
